# RDR2 Challenge Tracker

## Description
The RDR2 Challenge Tracker is a web application designed to help users track their progress in completing various challenges within the video game Red Dead Redemption 2 (RDR2). Users can create, update, and delete their progress on each challenge.

## Screenshot(s)
![Landing Page](/path/to/landing_page_screenshot.png)
<!-- Add any other screenshots here -->

## Technologies Used
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Passport.js (for authentication)
- EJS (Embedded JavaScript templates)

## Getting Started
To access the deployed app, visit [RDR2 Challenge Tracker](https://your-deployed-app-url.com).

To view the project planning and progress, check out our Trello board [here](https://trello.com/your-trello-board-url).

## Next Steps
- Implement a feature to allow users to share their progress on social media platforms.
- Add a feature to track statistics and achievements based on challenge completion.
- Integrate with the Rockstar Games Social Club API to sync challenges directly from the game.
